SUPER+W — Open wallpaper group selector (FZF picker)
ALT+W / ALT+SHIFT+W — Cycle wallpapers forward/backward in current group
wallpaper-select <group-name> — Set a group directly without the picker
Each group has a wallpaper.conf defining Matugen palette, mode, and DMS preset
Dynamic groups auto-extract colors from the wallpaper via Matugen
Custom groups apply hardware-branded DMS presets (ROG, Razer, Framework, etc.)
